<div class="container text-center m-5">
<h2>Welcome to Perfect Pals!👋</h2>

<p> Hi <strong><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>!</strong></p>
<p>Thank you for signing up. We are so happy to have you!</br>
  If you have any questions, comments or concerns, please reply to this email.</p>
<p>For now I encourage you to check out some of our Perfect Pals:</p>

<div style="margin: 16px;">
  <table style="width: 100%; border-spacing: 16px; border-collapse: separate;">
    <tr>
      <% User.take(4).each do |user| %>
        <td style="width: 25%; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; background-color: #fff; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
            <img src="<%= user.photo.attached? ? rails_blob_url(user.photo, only_path: false) : asset_path('default_avatar.png') %>" alt="User Photo" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;">
          </div>
          <h2 style="font-size: 18px; color: #333; margin: 0;"><%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %></h2>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin: 8px 0;"><%= user.location %></p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777; margin: 8px 0;"><%= user.bio&.truncate_words(15) %></p>
          <a href="<%= user_url(user) %>" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none;">View Profile</a>
        </td>
      <% end %>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>


<p>Happy searching for trustworthy connections!🧑‍🦰👨‍🦰👩‍🦰</p>

Margo
</div>
